# Design system documentation

Applies when editing **`docs/design-system/**/*.md`**.

## Authority

- **`AGENTS.md` §7** — product contract for tokens and primitives.
- **Code truth:** [`app/globals.css`](../../app/globals.css), [`lib/design-system.ts`](../../lib/design-system.ts), [`components/ui/`](../../components/ui/).
- Class-level UI contracts are enforced in **`design-system-enforcement.mdc`**; this file keeps docs in sync.

## Rules

- Do not document token names, variant strings, or CSS variables that are not implemented in code.
- When primitive APIs or tokens change, update `docs/design-system/figma-code-connect-mapping.md` in the same change when possible.
- Prefer documenting existing contracts over introducing new terminology.
